title.narrative: Cultivated land under the targeted value chain increases by 10% at the end of the project period for targeted beneficiaries
50% of target beneficiaries (of which 50% must women) for the selected value chain increase their production by at least 20% by theend of the Project
50% of target beneficiaries for the selected value chain increase their sales by at least 10% by the end of the Project

target.value: 80% of respondents are aware of the grant and 90% have positive view of grant mechanism

title.narrative: Development of seed, fertilizer and pesticide laws and regulations

target.value: Laws drafted and passed by parliament

title.narrative: Harmonization of policies and regulations governing the formation and regularization of farmer based groups

actual.value: NaFFSL constitution reviewed; CMMU transformed into Board through Act of Parliament

title.narrative: Beneficiary scorecards report satisfaction with project
Producers have access to at least one new market infrastructure
Real Farm gate prices increase by at least 10% for the selected value chains of targetted beneficiaries

baseline.value: Rice 58,500Le/50kg; Cassava Le6000/50kg; -Cocoa Le1550/50kg; -Palm oil Le24100/Batta

title.narrative: Beneficiary FBO's are run effectively for their members

baseline.value: Zero ( all farmers are members of national farmers association, but it does not address their needs)

target.value: 100% of beneficiary FBOs gets 80% approval rating

title.narrative: FBO's maintain records of membership dues, production levels, assets records
Time taken to transport goods to the nearest market reduced by 20% after rehabilitation of selected feeder road
Producers confirm firm supply and contractual agreements with marketers/ processors for the selected value chains of targeted beneficiaries

target.value: At least 60% of producers have contractual agreements with marketers

title.narrative: Volume of export of selected value chain commodities increased by 10% for targeted beneficiaries
Improved planting materials made available to 50% of targeted beneficiaries for the selected value chains

target.value: 50% of FBOs received improved planting materials
